MULTIPOLITY DESIGN — Per-Faction Shadow / Macro State
=====================================================
READ-ONLY research note (2026-06-16). No source changes implied.
Scope: evolve Civis from one civilization wearing N faction hats toward
distinct polities, each with its own macro scalars and shadow aggregates.

